    <h1 class="about-hero-title reveal reveal-delay-1">
      Built on trade.<br>Grown on <em>trust.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="about-hero-desc reveal reveal-delay-2">
      Over four decades of family craftsmanship, commercial construction,
